r or prefer a comprehensive web user interface for hands-on interaction – or something in between – we can help.​ NOTE: Payable Solutions are available in Commercial Center and Small Business Center.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66d75e0f8\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Automated Clearing House (ACH) Payment Origination\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"Significantly improve control of your business’ cash, funds availability, transaction reconciliation and cash forecasting with same-day or next-day ACH origination. ACH is a reliable and cost effective funds transfer method and is most often used for:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Business-to-business payments<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Direct deposit for payroll<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Federal, state, and local tax payments<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Non-immediate transfer of funds between accounts at other financial institutions<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nTBK Bank’s Desktop Delivery module within Commercial Center provides secure file transfer and self-guided mapping tools to support ERP and Treasury workstation integration with:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Unattended file delivery<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>File scheduling<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Straight-through processing<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Automated transaction confirmations<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Dual approvals<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Access via your own company’s compatible FTP solution<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66ed5e0f9\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Same Day ACH Origination\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"Same-day ACH can be used for those times when funds must be there today. To process as a same-day transaction, your ACH file must be submitted prior to the 10:00 am CST deadline. There are additional eligibility requirements for same-day transactions, including:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Transactions must be &lt; $25,000<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Domestic ACH only<span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\"> <\\/span>(International ACH ineligible)<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nMust have access through Commercial Center or Small Business Center.\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66f55e0fa\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Wire Transfers\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"When time is of the essence, TBK Bank’s Commercial Center and Small Business Center services are here for you. Move money from one institution to another, across town or across the world.\\r\\n\\r\\nWire transfer origination through our secure online platforms is efficient and safe. No more trips to the bank or paper forms to submit.\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Immediate<span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\"> <\\/span>transfer of funds<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Guaranteed settlement<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Commercial Center offers:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Domestic wire origination<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>International wire origination (USD)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>FX wire origination<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Small Business Center offers:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Domestic wire origination<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\nTBK Bank’s Desktop Delivery module within Commercial Center provides secure file transfer options for high volume wire processors. Map to a Fed-formatted file or an ISO 20022 standard format. For non-standard formats, Commercial Center includes a self-guided mapping tool to support ERP and Treasury workstation integration.<span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\"> <\\/span>Other features include:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Unattended file delivery<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>File scheduling<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Straight-through processing<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Automated transaction confirmations<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Dual approvals<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Access via your own company’s compatible FTP solution<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66f75e0fb\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Purchasing Card\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"One Card is ideal for businesses needing maximum control over expenses.<span class=\\\"Apple-converted-space\\\"> <\\/span>Manage travel and entertainment expenses, business purchases, utilities, fleet transactions and more. The program includes a secure online portal with real time access to your card program:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Worldwide acceptance<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Manage cardholder limits and purchases<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Maintain spending controls in real-time<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Protect against card misuse<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Advanced administrative tools and reporting<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Flexible billing options<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Tax and compliance management support<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Import transaction detail for simplified reconciliation with your accounting or Treasury Workstation<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n<!-- /wp:acf/wrapper -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/banner {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fa9c4e038ce5\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/banner\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"alignment\": \"center\",\n        \"_alignment\": \"field_5f8f4c162afd4\",\n        \