, and helps manage your expenses, again, all in one place.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TBK Bank supports Web Connect for Quicken. Go to&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.quicken.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:www.quicken.com/</a>&nbsp;or check out an authorized retailer to get the right Quicken products for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>QuickBooks</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For TBK business clients using QuickBooks, we offer WebConnect for QuickBooks.&nbsp;Log in to Commercial Center or Small Business Center and export your transactions directly into QuickBooks. Save time reconciling financial transactions and manage your money with ease.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Does TBK Bank offer DirectConnect to QuickBooks?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Commercial Center and Small Business Center offer the Web Connect method of integrating with QuickBooks. Log in and export transactions to QuickBooks.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Because we use the most advanced security, Direct Connect with QuickBooks is not yet compatible with a soft token or Multi-Factor Authentication.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:acf/wrapper -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/banner {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fa9c4e038ce5\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/banner\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"alignment\": \"center\",\n        \"_alignment\": \"field_5f8f4c162afd4\",\n        \"copy\": \"<h2>Open an account with TBK Bank<\\/h2>\\r\\nLet\'s open up new possibilities for your business.\",\n        \"_copy\": \"field_5f57ece16621e\",\n        \"links_0_link\": {\n            \"title\": \"Open An Account\",\n            \"url\": \"\\/our-bank\\/apply-for-an-account\\/\",\n            \"target\": \"_blank\"\n        },\n        \"_links_0_link\": \"field_5f60b46f4693f\",\n       