tolen debit card, please call 1-800-472-3272.<br>Traveling internationally? Contact your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tbkbank.com/our-bank/locations/\">local branch</a>&nbsp;so your transactions aren’t blocked.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66d75e0f8\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Fraud Text Alerts\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"With text fraud alerts, if our system detects suspicious activity on your card, you will receive a text message with details about the suspected transaction. All you have to do is respond to the text with a “yes” or “no” to confirm or deny the transaction. If you indicate the transaction is fraud, you’ll receive another message with a number to call for follow-up. If not, you are all set. The system will mark the transaction as legitimate and you can get on with your day- simple as that. And best of all this service is complimentary for all TBK Bank Debit Card holders, you simply need to enroll. Please contact a personal banker to enroll in fraud text alerts, you must have a mobile phone number and an active debit card.\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Text notification when fraudulent card activity is detected<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Validate authorized transactions to continue card usage without disruption<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Confirmed fraudulent transactions can help block additional transactions and stop fraud<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66ed5e0f9\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Image Card\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"Show off your creative side with a custom image card of your own design. Select an option below to start creating:\\r\\n\\r\\nIf your Debit Card begins with 520271 <a class=\\\"confirm outbound-link\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/us.personalcard.net\\/AllAboutMe\\/Designer\\/PCS\\/Start.aspx?Handover_Key=34e6eae5-5cd9-4c19-92ce-b59c3c4a54b3&amp;LanguageId=en-US\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" aria-label=\\\"click here if your debit card begins with 520271\\\">click here<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\nIf your Debit Card begins with 520272 <a class=\\\"confirm outbound-link\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/us.personalcard.net\\/AllAboutMe\\/Designer\\/PCS\\/Start.aspx?Handover_Key=c82841e0-9246-49a6-84b6-314b2a2fd328&amp;LanguageId=en-US\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\" aria-label=\\\"click here if your debit cards begins with 520272\\\">click here<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lxvh1219qb82jz0st1psmii1-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/ImageCardTermsandConditions-1.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Terms and Conditions<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lxvh1219qb82jz0st1psmii1-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/10\\/Image-Card-Frequently-Asked-Questions.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Frequently Asked Questions<\\/a>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lxvh1219qb82jz0st1psmii1-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/ImageCardGuidelines-1.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">Image Guidelines​<\\/a>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66f55e0fa\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"CardValet®\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"Not using your card? Turn it off! Control access to your debit card through the TBK Bank mobile app and CardVale