 you see your money, all in one place. Connect all of your accounts, create realistic budgets, and manage your expenses, again, all in one place.\\r\\n\\r\\nTBK Bank supports Direct Connect and Web Connect for Quicken. Go to <a class=\\\"outbound-link\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.quicken.com\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">http:\\/\\/www.quicken.com\\/<\\/a>, or check out an authorized retailer, to get the right Quicken products for you.​\\r\\n\\r\\n<a class=\\\"btn-primary__rounded green\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tbkbank.com\\/our-bank\\/contact-us\\/\\\" aria-label=\\\"\\\">Request Info<\\/a>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66f55e0fa\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Quickbooks\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"Integrating QuickBooks and your TBK Bank account is an easy way to check balances, create customizable financial reports, and much more. QuickBooks offers accounting applications and allows business to accept and make payments, manage and pay bills, and payroll functions. TBK Bank proudly supports Web Connect for QuickBooks.\\r\\n\\r\\nVisit <a class=\\\"outbound-link\\\" href=\\\"http:\\/\\/quickbooks.com\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">http:\\/\\/quickbooks.com\\/<\\/a>, or an authorized retailer, to select the Quickbooks product meets your needs.\\r\\n\\r\\n<a class=\\\"btn-primary__rounded green\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tbkbank.com\\/our-bank\\/contact-us\\/\\\" aria-label=\\\"\\\">Request Info<\\/a>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66f75e0fb\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand