r\": \"Estatements\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"Stop filing. Start smiling. To make your life easier, we’ve made eStatements available on all TBK Bank accounts, free of charge. It’s the exact same information as your paper statement, only in digital file.\\r\\n\\r\\nThey’re also instantly retrievable and are a great way to keep your data more secure (identity thieves love a good paper trail).\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Simplify account management<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Eliminate paper waste<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Safer than mailed paper statements*<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Save\\/download\\/print as needed<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Available 24\\/7 online<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Easy retrieval<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Check images provided<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Absolutely free<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<em data-redactor-tag=\\\"em\\\">*Experts indicate that most identity theft occurs at home, including stealing documents from mailboxes and garbage cans.<\\/em>\\r\\n\\r\\n<em><a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lxvh1219qb82jz0st1psmii1-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/08\\/eStatement-Disclosure-and-Consent-Agreement.pdf\\\">eStatement Terms and Conditions<\\/a><\\/em>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a class=\\\"btn-primary__rounded green outbound-link\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/lxvh1219qb82jz0st1psmii1-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/06\\/eStatements_Signup.pdf\\\" aria-label=\\\"how to enroll document\\\">How To Enroll<\\/a>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66ed5e0f9\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Bill Pay\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"​The only way to make paying bills easier to swallow is to just make it easier. And that’s exactly what TBK Bank Bill Pay does.\\r\\n\\r\\n​Schedule recurring payments, set up email alerts for your banking activity, even make payments in advance. Electronically. Whenever you’d like.\\r\\n\\r\\nNo stamps. Just a simpler, better way to handle your bills.\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>​Available with all checking accounts<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Available 24\\/7 online<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Receive bills electronically<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Set up bill reminders<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Payments post faster than mailing<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>See your payment history online<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Securely encrypted<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Save on stamps​​<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<a class=\\\"btn-primary__rounded green\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/tbkbank.com\\/frequently-asked-questions\\/?section=online-bill-pay\\\" aria-label=\\\"\\\">FAQS<\\/a>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66f55e0fa\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"ZELLE®\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"<em>Zelle<\\/em>® is a convenient way to send money using your mobile banking app or online banking account.\\r\\n\\r\\nWhether it’s saving you a trip to the ATM or taking out the guesswork of divvying up the lunch tab, <em>Zelle<\\/em> is a fast, safe and easy way to send and request money. Funds are sent directly to the recipient’s account in a matter of minutes<sup>1<\\/sup>, and all you need is the recipient’s email address or U.S. mobile phone number.\\r\\n\\r\\n<a class=\\\"btn-primary__rounded green\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/tbkbank.com\\/zelle\\/\\\" aria-label=\\\"learn more about zelle\\\">Learn More<\\/a>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66f75e0fb\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\