tolen debit card, please call 1-800-472-3272.<br>Traveling internationally? Contact your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tbkbank.com/our-bank/locations/\">local branch</a>&nbsp;so your transactions aren’t blocked.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66d75e0f8\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Fraud Text Alerts\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"With text fraud alerts, if our system detects suspicious activity on your card, you will receive a text message with details about the suspected transaction. All you have to do is respond to the text with a “yes” or “no” to confirm or deny the transaction. If you indicate the transaction is fraud, you’ll receive another message with a number to call for follow-up. If not, you are all set. The system will mark the transaction as legitimate and you can get on with your day- simple as that. And best of all this service is complimentary for all TBK Bank Debit Card holders, you simply need to enroll. Please contact a personal banker to enroll in fraud text alerts, you must have a mobile phone number and an active debit card.\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Text notification when fraudulent card activity is detected<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Validate authorized transactions to continue card usage without disruption<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Confirmed fraudulent transactions can help block additional transactions and stop fraud<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fac66ed5e0f9\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Image Card\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"Show off your creative side with a custom imag