tolen bases don’t just help the River Bandits on the scoreboard, they also help strike out homelessness in our community.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For a complete schedule of River Bandits games, click&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.milb.com/quad-cities/schedule/2019-04\">here</a>!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>More About Humility Homes and Services</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Humility Homes and Services, Inc. is committed to ending homelessness by offering housing opportunities and supportive services in the greater Quad Cities area. They own 18 properties in Davenport, IA, which includes 41 apartments, a 10,000 square foot Fresh Start Donation Center and lease an additional 52 apartments. They also have a 70 bed, low-barrier, emergency shelter serving women and men 18 years of age and older. On any given day, 250 – 300 adults and children are participating in their services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For more information about this great organization visit their website at&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.humilityhomes.org/\">www.humilityhomes.org</a>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":null} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":5571,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img src=\"http://tbknew.local/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/HHAS-Logo.png\" alt=\"HHAS logo\" class=\"wp-image-5571\"/></figure></div>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:image {\"align\":\"center\",\"id\":5573,\"sizeSlug\"