(5594,	1,	'2020-11-17 21:40:21',	'2020-11-17 21:40:21',	'<!-- wp:acf/hero {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fb41c5208383\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/hero\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"slides_0_copy\": \"<h1>About Us<\\/h1>\",\n        \"_slides_0_copy\": \"field_5f5a554438a1d\",\n        \"slides_0_links\": \"\",\n        \"_slides_0_links\": \"field_5f5a54cf0eb62\",\n        \"slides_0_corner_cross_hair\": \"0\",\n        \"_slides_0_corner_cross_hair\": \"field_5f6359aee2184\",\n        \"slides_0_show_app_icons\": \"0\",\n        \"_slides_0_show_app_icons\": \"field_5f620cd9dc17a\",\n        \"slides_0_background_color\": \"image\",\n        \"_slides_0_background_color\": \"field_5f5a559d9132a\",\n        \"slides_0_background_image\": 5579,\n        \"_slides_0_background_image\": \"field_5f5a55a39132b\",\n        \"slides_0_background_darkness_overlay\": \"40\",\n        \"_slides_0_background_darkness_overlay\": \"field_5f723199fa570\",\n        \"slides\": 1,\n        \"_slides\": \"field_5f5a552f38a1c\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/checkerboard {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fb41d2c08386\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/checkerboard\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"rows_0_image\": 5114,\n        \"_rows_0_image\": \"field_5f75e2bd0cea8\",\n        \"rows_0_copy\": \"<h2 class=\\\"title\\\">About TBK Bank<\\/h2>\\r\\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\\r\\n\\r\\nTBK Bank, SSB, is a subsidiary of Triumph Bancorp, Inc., a Texas-state savings bank headquartered in Dallas, Texas. We offer consumer and commercial banking products from our 18 branches throughout eastern Iowa and Illinois and 43 branches throughout Colorado, western Kansas and New Mexico. We also have two branches located in Dallas.\\r\\n\\r\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph --> <!-- wp:paragraph -->\\r\\n\\r\\nOur lending capabilities include commercial real estate, mortgage warehouse lending and other general business lending.\\r\\n\\r\\n<!-- \\/wp:paragraph --> <!-- wp:paragraph -->\\r\\n\\r\\nThrough our division of <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.triumphcf.com\\/\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noreferrer noopener\\\">Triumph Commercial Finance<\\/a> we offer asset based lending and equipment finance throughout the United States.<!-- \\/wp:paragraph -->\",\n        \"_rows_0_copy\": \"field_5f75e2c70cea9\",\n        \"rows_0_background_color\": \"primary\",\n        \"_rows_0_background_color\": \"field_5f75f06fa8ddb\",\n        \"rows_1_image\": 5581,\n        \"_rows_1_image\": \"field_5f75e2bd0cea8\",\n        \"rows_1_copy\": \"<h2 class=\\\"title\\\">COMMUNITY INVOLVEMENT<\\/h2>\\r\\nFrom the greatest moments to the everyday moments, TBK Bank prides ourselves on being there for our customers and our communities every step of the way. We’re made up of your friends and neighbors, people you know and trust, people who value you and the important things in your life.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe are proud to support numerous charities and civic organizations within the communities we serve. In addition to financial contributions, our team members take pride in giving back personally through countless volunteer hours. Our team members participate in local service organizations, festivals and events, as well as serving on the boards of directors and committees at many area schools, hospitals, and community groups.\\r\\n\\r\\nOur communities will always remain in the fabric of our mission.\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/tbkbank.com\\/our-bank\\/community-involvement\\/\\\">LEARN MORE ABOUT OUR COMMUNITY INVOLVEMENT<\\/a>\",\n        \"_rows_1_copy\": \"field_5f75e2c70cea9\",\n        \"rows_1_background_color\": \"primary\",\n        \"_rows_1_background_color\": \"field_5f75f06fa8ddb\",\n        \"rows_2_image\": 5535,\n        \"_rows_2_image\": \"field_5f75e2bd0cea8\",\n        \"rows_2_copy\": \"<h2>Our Mission<\\/h2>\\r\\nAs a member of the Triumph Bancorp, Inc. group, (Nasdaq: TBK), we share Triumph’s vision to be the most valuable company in our industry. To be valuable is to make a lasting and positive impact on all that we touch and do by:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Investing in the development and success of our team members<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Meeting the financial needs of our customers<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Making profits for our shareholders<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Managing risk through cycles<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Improving the world around us<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n        \"_rows_2_copy\": \"field_5f75e2c70cea9\",\n        \"rows_2_background_color\": \"primary\",\n        \"_rows_2_background_color\": \"field_5f75f06fa8ddb\",\n        \"rows\": 3,\n        \"_rows\": \"field_5f75e2a70cea7\",\n        \"show_layout_options\": \"0\",\n        \"_show_layout_options\": \"field_5f579b546ee17\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/wrapper {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fb41cfe08385\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/wrapper\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"generous_vertical_padding\": \"0\",\n        \"_generous_vertical_padding\": \"field_5f6e04852a13b\",\n        \"show_layout_options\": \"1\",\n        \"_show_layout_options\": \"field_5f579b546ee17\",\n        \"width\": \"container-md\",\n        \"_width\": \"field_5f5798a171a9f\",\n        \"background_color\": \"white\",\n        \"_background_color\": \"field_5f57993c71aa0\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"\",\n    \"mode\": \"preview\"\n} -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>What does TBK Bank stand for?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TBK is our stock ticker symbol, but TBK stands for much more. We stand for excellence. What started from humble beginnings has grown into a bank with small-town values and the resources to make a difference. We are a bank that stands for you.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TBK stands for rolling up our sleeves on behalf of our customers, because that’s what they deserve.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TBK stands for lending a helping hand to individuals, small business owners, and entrepreneurs, because we’ve been there.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TBK stands for investing in our communities, because that’s what neighbors do.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With team members ready to answer everyday questions, to the latest technology that makes banking more convenient, TBK Bank stands for helping the people and businesses in our communities succeed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://tbkbank.com/our-bank/careers/\">JOIN THE TBK BANK TEAM</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:acf/wrapper -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/content-grid {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fb420040838a\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/content-grid\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"grid_copy\": \"<h2 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\">Executive Team<\\/h2>\",\n        \"_grid_copy\": \"field_5f6d1a5e670a6\",\n        \"grid_copy_width\": \"container-sm\",\n        \"_grid_copy_width\": \"field_5f6d1aed0d97b\",\n        \"grid_max_columns\": \"3\",\n        \"_grid_max_columns\": \"field_5f8de990189b7\",\n        \"grid_item_style\": \"default\",\n        \"_grid_item_style\": \"field_5f6cf17589d27\",\n        \"grid_item_image_style\": \"image\",\n        \"_grid_item_image_style\": \"field_5f6d1e3a172c9\",\n        \"grid_item_image_link\": \"0\",\n        \"_grid_item_image_link\": \"field_5f89b16cc6d58\",\n        \"grid_item_alignment\": \"center\",\n        \"_grid_item_alignment\": \"field_5f6d11d78e3bc\",\n        \"grid_items_0_image\": 5585,\n        \"_grid_items_0_image\": \"field_5f6cf27289d29\",\n        \"grid_items_0_copy\": \"<h3 class=\\\"name text-center\\\">Aaron P. Graft<\\/h3>\\r\\n<p class=\\\"simple\\\">VICE CHAIRMAN, CHIEF EXECUTIVE OFFICER AND PUBLIC INFORMATION OFFICER<\\/p>\",\n        \"_grid_items_0_copy\": \"field_5f6cf28989d2a\",\n        \"grid_items_0_link_link\": \"\",\n        \"_grid_items_0_link_link\": \"field_5f6cf2e489d2c\",\n     