(5670,	1,	'2020-11-20 21:42:26',	'2020-11-20 21:42:26',	'<!-- wp:acf/wrapper {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fb838c59d008\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/wrapper\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"generous_vertical_padding\": \"0\",\n        \"_generous_vertical_padding\": \"field_5f6e04852a13b\",\n        \"show_layout_options\": \"1\",\n        \"_show_layout_options\": \"field_5f579b546ee17\",\n        \"width\": \"container-lg\",\n        \"_width\": \"field_5f5798a171a9f\",\n        \"background_color\": \"transparent\",\n        \"_background_color\": \"field_5f57993c71aa0\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"\",\n    \"mode\": \"preview\"\n} -->\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":1} -->\n<h1>Go Local – Official Rules</h1>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>NO PURCHASE OR ACCOUNT OPENING IS NECESSARY TO ENTER OR WIN THE DRAWING. VOID WHERE PROHIBITED BY LAW. IMPORTANT: PLEASE READ THESE OFFICIAL RULES, WHICH ARE A CONTRACT, CAREFULLY BEFORE ENTERING THIS DRAWING. BY PARTICIPATING IN THE DRAWING, YOU AGREE TO BE BOUND BY THESE OFFICIAL RULES AND REPRESENT THAT YOU SATISFY ALL OF THE ELIGIBILITY REQUIREMENTS BELOW.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>EACH WINNER WILL BE REQUIRED TO RESPOND TO WINNER NOTIFICATION AND OTHER COMMUNICATIONS WITHIN THREE (3) BUSINESS DAYS OR OTHER TIME FRAME STATED IN THE WINNER NOTIFICATION OR OTHER COMMUNICATION FROM TBK BANK, SSB OR PRIZE MAY BE FORFEITED.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>SUMMARY AND ENTRY PERIOD</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>“2020 Go Local Drawing” Drawing (“Drawing”) starts at 12:00 a.m. Central Time (“CT”) on October 15th, 2020 and ends at 11:59 p.m. CT on December 20th, 2020 (“Drawing Period”). By participating in the Drawing, each entrant unconditionally accepts and agrees to comply with and abide by these Official Rules (the “Official Rules”), and the decisions of TBK BANK, SSB and its subsidiaries (“TBK Bank”), including the interpretation of these Official Rules, which will be final and binding in all respects.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Eligible individuals (see ELIGIBILITY section of these Official Rules below) may enter the Drawing as defined below:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list {\"ordered\":true} -->\n<ol><li>Complete the TBK Bank Go Local Entry Form Online OR</li><li>Write your name, address, city, state, zip, and phone number with area code on a 3.5 inch by 5 inch index card and mail it to:<br>Go Local With TBK Bank TBK Bank, SSB<br>PO Box 1030 Bettendorf, IA 52722<br>USPS mailed entries must be postmarked between October 15, 2020 and December 20, 2020</li></ol>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>ELIGIBILITY AND LIMITATIONS</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Participants and winner(s) must be U.S. residents at least 18- years old or as determined by TBK Bank. Only one (1) prize per household for the Drawing. Only one (1) prize per household within any thirty (30) day period. Employees of TBK Bank, or its subsidiaries, and members of the immediate family of any such persons are not eligible to participate and win. The term “immediate family” includes spouses, siblings, parents, children, grandparents, and grandchildren, whether as in-laws, or by current or past marriage(s), remarriage(s), adoption, co-habitation or other family extension, and any other persons residing at the same household whether or not related.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>PRIZE(S):</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><li>One (1) $500 Visa Gift Card</li></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>DELIVERY OF PRIZE(S)</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The prize will be picked up in person at an agreed upon Triumph Community Bank branch during normal business hours.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>WINNER SELECTION/NOTIFICATION</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Winner(s) will be selected, subject to verification, in a random drawing from all eligible entries received regardless of method of entry, to be held on or about December 21, 2020. Within approximately two (2) business days after the winner selection,&nbsp;TBK Bank will attempt to notify potential winner(s) that he/she/they may have won a prize by private Facebook message. Each winner will be required to respond to winner notification and other communications within three (3) business days or other time frame stated in the winner notification or other communication from TBK Bank or prize may be forfeited. Winner name(s) may be posted on TBK Bank’s website and/or Facebook page at their sole discretion. If any prize, prize notification, or Drawing-related communication is rejected, faulty, or returned as undeliverable, if a potential winner does not respond according to the notification’s or TBK Bank’s instructions, or if a winner or potential winner fails to comply with these Official Rules, the prize will be forfeited and an alternate winner may be selected (time permitting) based on the original method of winner selection. TBK Bank is not obligated to pursue more than three (3) alternate winners for any prize for any reason, in which case a prize may be deemed unclaimed and TBK Bank will have no further obligation with respect to that prize.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>RELEASES, TAXES AND MISCELLANEOUS</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>PUBLICITY; PRIVACY.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By participating, all participants and winner(s) grant TBK Bank exclusive permission to use their names, characters, photographs, voices, and likenesses in connection with promotion of this and other contests and waive any claims to royalty, right, or remuneration or such use.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>RELEASE.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By participating in the Drawing, each participant and winner waives any and all claims of liability against TBK Bank, SSB, its parent, subsidiaries, affiliates, and each of their respective officers, directors, employees, and agents, for any personal injury or loss which may occur from the conduct of, or participation in, the Drawing, or from the use of any prize. In order to receive a prize, participants must sign an official waiver form provided by TBK Bank.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>TAXES.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Any valuation of the prize(s) stated above is based on available information provided to TBK Bank, and the value of any prize awarded to a winner may be reported for tax purposes as required by law. Each winner is solely responsible for reporting and paying any and all applicable taxes. Each winner must provide TBK Bank, if requested, with valid identification and a valid taxpayer identification number or social security number before any prize will be awarded. Prizes are not transferable, redeemable for cash or exchangeable for any other prize. Any person winning over $10.00 in prizes from TBK Bank will receive an IRS form 1099 at the end of the calendar year and a copy of such form will be filed with the IRS.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>DECISIONS.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>By participating in the Drawing, participants agree to be bound by the decisions of TBK Bank personnel. TBK Bank reserves the right to disqualify any participant or winner and may refuse to award any prize to a person who is ineligible or has violated any rule, gained unfair advantage in participating in the Drawing, or obtained winner status using fraudulent means. TBK Bank will interpret these rules and resolve any disputes, conflicting claims or ambiguities concerning the rules or the Drawing and TBK Bank’s decisions concerning such disputes shall be final. If the conduct or outcome of the Drawing is affected by human error, any mechanical, technical, electronic, communications, telephone, computer, hardware or software errors, malfunctions or failures of any kind, intentional interference or any event beyond the control of TBK Bank, TBK Bank reserves the right to terminate this Drawing, or make such other decisions regarding the outcome TBK Bank deems appropriate. All decisions will be made by TBK Bank and are final. TBK Bank may waive any of these rules in its sole discretion.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>MISCELLANEOUS.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Each winner must submit proof of eligibility and sign TBK Bank’s release form to claim the prize. No purchase necessary to participate or win. Void where prohibited. Odds ofwinning depend upon the number of participants. TBK Bank may substitute prizes of equivalent value, amend the rules or discontinue the Drawing at any time as announced. TBK Bank disclaims any responsibility to notify participants of any aspect related to the conduct of the<br>Drawing. Written copies of these rules are available during normal business hours at each branch office of TBK Bank and by mail upon written request with a stamped, self-addressed return envelope. All entries become the property of TBK Bank and will not be returned.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Winner is responsible for any and all other costs and expenses not listed herein as being provided, including but not limited to transportation to/from venue, hotel accommodations, meals, hotel incidentals, parking, souvenirs, gratuities, any personal expenses. Any prize details not specified above will be determined by TBK Bank, in its sole discretion. TBK Bank will not be liable for any expenses incurred as a consequence of event cancellations or delays. TBK Bank will not replace any lost or stolen prizes or prize components. Prize is awarded “as is” without any warranty or guaranty, either express of implied by TBK Bank.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3>COMPLIANCE WITH LAW.</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The conduct of the Drawing is governed by the applicable laws of the United States of America and the State of Texas, which take precedence over any rule to the contrary herein. TBK Bank shall follow the applicable laws for conducting contests, including notice to the state attorney general or consumer affairs office, posting of a prize bond, furnishing lists of winners, providing specific written information about the Drawing, etc. as required by local and state law.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:acf/wrapper -->',	'Official Rules',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'official-rules',	'',	'',	'2020-11-20 21:47:37',	'2020-11-20 21:47:37',	'',	5669,	'http://tbknew.local/?page_id=5670',	0,	'page',	'',	0),
