s to take your challenge as our own. We would like to earn your business by providing a high-level of customer service with experienced community bankers.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>On September 8, 2018, First National Bank of Durango merged into TBK Bank, SSB. All accounts with First National Bank of Durango will convert into a TBK Bank account beginning the close of business on December 7, 2018.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Until then, please use FNBDurango.com for all your banking needs. If you are a current customer details about your account’s conversion will be mailed to you. If you have any questions please stop by your local branch or click here for current customer conversion related FAQ’s. We look forward to serving you as TBK Bank!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Curious to know more about TBK Bank?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please&nbsp;<a href=\"https://tbkbank.com/\">click here</a>&nbsp;to visit TBKBank.com.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Wondering what TBK stands for?</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s a question we get asked a lot. Simply put, TBK is our stock ticker symbol, but TBK Bank stands for much more. To truly understand what TBK Bank stands for come into one of our locations to experience it for yourself. TBK stands for helping the people and businesses in our communities succeed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:html -->\n<br>\n<!-- /wp:html -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Welcome to TBK Bank, SSB</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:acf/wrapper -->',	'Welcome',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'welcomefnbd',	'',	'',	'2020-11-23 18:20:35',	'2020-11-23 18:20:35',	''