(5736,	1,	'2020-11-23 19:49:53',	'2020-11-23 19:49:53',	'<!-- wp:acf/hero {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc1202a1062\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/hero\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"slides_0_copy\": \"<h1>COVID-19 Information<\\/h1>\\r\\nLast updated: August 27, 2020\",\n        \"_slides_0_copy\": \"field_5f5a554438a1d\",\n        \"slides_0_links\": \"\",\n        \"_slides_0_links\": \"field_5f5a54cf0eb62\",\n        \"slides_0_corner_cross_hair\": \"0\",\n        \"_slides_0_corner_cross_hair\": \"field_5f6359aee2184\",\n        \"slides_0_show_app_icons\": \"0\",\n        \"_slides_0_show_app_icons\": \"field_5f620cd9dc17a\",\n        \"slides_0_background_color\": \"image\",\n        \"_slides_0_background_color\": \"field_5f5a559d9132a\",\n        \"slides_0_background_image\": 5686,\n        \"_slides_0_background_image\": \"field_5f5a55a39132b\",\n        \"slides_0_background_darkness_overlay\": \"30\",\n        \"_slides_0_background_darkness_overlay\": \"field_5f723199fa570\",\n        \"slides\": 1,\n        \"_slides\": \"field_5f5a552f38a1c\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/wrapper {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc129fa1066\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/wrapper\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"generous_vertical_padding\": \"0\",\n        \"_generous_vertical_padding\": \"field_5f6e04852a13b\",\n        \"show_layout_options\": \"1\",\n        \"_show_layout_options\": \"field_5f579b546ee17\",\n        \"width\": \"container-md\",\n        \"_width\": \"field_5f5798a171a9f\",\n        \"background_color\": \"transparent\",\n        \"_background_color\": \"field_5f57993c71aa0\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"\",\n    \"mode\": \"preview\"\n} -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>We\'re Here To Help</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ensuring the health and safety of our customers, team members and the communities we serve is our top priority. Below you will find ways we are here to help you as we work to keep each other safe and make sure you still have access to your accounts and banking services.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc12a3a1067\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Find A Location\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"<h4>Branch, Drive-Thru Or ATM<\\/h4>\\r\\nTo find an open branch, drive-thru or ATM location, please visit our\\r\\n<a href=\\\"\\/our-bank\\/locations\\/\\\">locations page<\\/a>.\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc12bfa1068\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Keeping You Safe\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"<h4>Ensuring Health And Safety Remain A Top Priority<\\/h4>\\r\\nEnsuring the health and safety of our customers, team members and the communities we serve is our top priority. We continue to actively monitor the COVID-19 situation from the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.cdc.gov\\/coronavirus\\/2019-ncov\\/index.html\\\">Center of Disease Control and Prevention<\\/a> (CDC) and the <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.who.int\\/\\\">World Health Organization<\\/a> (WHO) to ensure we are able to act on the latest information and guidelines. Rest assured, we continue to ensure you have access to your accounts and banking services. We also want to remind you of the many alternative ways we can serve your banking needs during this time.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you have been negatively impacted by the coronavirus and need assistance with your loan or deposit account please contact Customer Care at <a href=\\\"tel:8666443935\\\">866-644-3935<\\/a> to talk with a TBK Bank representative.\\r\\n\\r\\nYou can also find out how we are providing financial assistance to our personal and business customers by reviewing the Customer Relief Efforts tab below. This includes our participation in the CARES Act (Coronavirus Aid, Relief and Economic Security Act), including Customer and Community Relief Efforts, the SBA Paycheck Participation program and Main Street Lending program.\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc12daa1069\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"How We Can Help\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"<h4>Customer And Community Relief Efforts<\\/h4>\\r\\nWith the recent passage of the CARES Act (Coronavirus Aid, Relief and Economic Security Act), we want you to know that TBK Bank is quickly working to understand how we can further support our personal and business customers. As more details of the Act are announced we will provide additional updates.\\r\\n<h4>Personal Banking Customers<\\/h4>\\r\\nTBK Bank is committed to helping our customers and communities in this time of need. If you have been negatively impacted by the coronavirus and need assistance with your deposit account please contact Customer Care at <a href=\\\"tel:8666443935\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">866-644-3935<\\/a> to talk with a TBK Bank representative.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>PERSONAL BANKING CUSTOMERS<\\/strong>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>We have increased our ATM daily deposit limit from $5,000 to $7,500 for both\\r\\npersonal and business customers.<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>We have increased our mobile deposit daily dollar amount, monthly dollar amount and\\r\\nitem count.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<strong>GOVERNMENT ISSUED STIMULUS CHECKS<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nWe are available to cash government issued stimulus checks for both customers and non-customers who have two forms of valid identification.\\r\\n\\r\\nWe continue to review how we can best serve our customers and communities during this time and will continue to provide you updates as this situation evolves.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you filed your taxes electronically in 2018 or 2019 you may have the opportunity to ACH deposit your stimulus check directly into your TBK Bank Account, please make sure you use the correct routing number: 111909579.\\r\\n\\r\\nAdditionally if you receive a physical stimulus check you can use mobile deposit in the TBK Bank Mobile App to deposit your check directly into your account and avoid going to a drive thru.\\r\\n\\r\\nMany customers have begun to receive stimulus payments via direct deposit to their TBK Bank accounts. To track your Economic Impact Payment, visit:\\r\\n<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.irs.gov\\/coronavirus\\/economic-impact-payments\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">www.irs.gov\\/coronavirus\\/economic-impact-payments<\\/a>, or check your balances in the TBK Bank Mobile App or Online Banking.\\r\\n\\r\\nFor more information on the government stimulus check program and eligibility visit: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.irs.gov\\/coronavirus\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">www.irs.gov\\/coronavirus<\\/a>\\r\\n<h4>Business And Commercial Banking Customers<\\/h4>\\r\\n<strong>PAYCHECK PROTECTION PROGRAM<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nIn order to assure we are able to process all of our current PPP applications, TBK Bank will stop accepting new PPP applications at 6:00 PM CST on August 6, 2020.\\r\\n\\r\\nTo date, we are proud to have been able to help over 2,000 local small businesses receive a total of $227 million in funding in the communities we serve.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you have not submitted a PPP application for your business or are not currently a TBK Bank customer and are interested in moving your banking relationship to TBK Bank, we would be honored to help you and your business through this PPP process, please reach out to a TBK Bank Relationship Manager or email:\\r\\n<a href=\\\"mailto:SBAtaskforce@tbkbank.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">SBAtaskforce@tbkbank.com<\\/a> as soon as possible to get started.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf TBK Bank has already processed a PPP loan for your small business, we will be reaching out in the upcoming months to complete your forgiveness application. Thank you for your patience as we await further guidance from the SBA.\\r\\nIf you have any questions or are looking for additional assistance options please contact your TBK Bank Relationship Manager or see our <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.tbkbank.com\\/covid-19-information\\/#\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">PPP FAQ<\\/a>.\\r\\n\\r\\n<em>The content on this page does not reflect any changes that could result from rules and regulations, as well as related guidance regarding the Paycheck Protection Program Flexibility Act of 2020 (PPPFA), which was signed into law on June 5, 2020. We expect additional guidance from the SBA prior to lenders implementing changes related to the PPPFA. In the event of any discrepancies between the information on this site and the SBA’s site, please follow official SBA guidance.<\\/em>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc130ca106a\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Bank From Home\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"<h4>Online, Mobile Or Phone – We’re Right Where You Need Us<\\/h4>\\r\\nTBK Bank has many ways you can banks safely from home with online banking, our mobile app or telephone banking.\\r\\n<h4>The TBK Bank Mobile App<\\/h4>\\r\\nGet secure and easy access to your accounts from your smartphone 24\\/7\\/365.\\r