accounts from a computer or tablet.\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>View your balance and transaction history<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Manage your budget and see all your finances, from TBK and other financial institutions<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Transfer funds from one account to another<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Pay your bills with Bill Pay<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Pay friends and family quickly and securely with Zelle (no cash or check necessary)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>View and download your statements (with eStatements)<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Manage your credit score<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/web15.secureinternetbank.com\\/PBI_PBI1151\\/login\\/111909579\\/\\\">Login to Online Banking<\\/a>\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/web15.secureinternetbank.com\\/PBI_PBI1151\\/Enroll\\/111909579\\\">Sign Up for Online Banking<\\/a> (Account Number is Required)\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Telephone Banking<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"tel:8773214347\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">877-321-4347<\\/a>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Check Your Balance<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Make Transfers<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc135821e13\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"For Your Business\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"<h4>With Service And Expertise – Our Team Remains Ready To Help<\\/h4>\\r\\nOur robust suite of products and services can convert everyday transactions to electronic ones to help you easily manage your business from home, such as payroll, bill payment and faster collection of accounts receivable.\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n \\t<li>Commercial and Small Business Center Online Account Management<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>The TBK Bank Business Mobile App<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Remote Deposit Capture<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Merchant Services to collect Credit Card Transactions<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>ACH Origination for Both Credit and Debits<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>Direct Deposit for your Employees<\\/li>\\r\\n \\t<li>ACH Payments for Your Customers<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n&nbsp;\\r\\n<h4>Treasury Management Customers<\\/h4>\\r\\nOur Treasury Management team is here to help. We are operating as usual. While we do not anticipate any disruptions in service for Commercial or Small Business Center, we will communicate to customers immediately through a Communication Bulletin in your Commercial or Small Business Center online banking menu.\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you have any questions or concerns, please contact Treasury Support Monday through Friday 8:00 AM to 6:00 PM CST by emailing <a href=\\\"mailto:tm@tbkbank.com\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener\\\">tm@tbkbank.com<\\/a> or by calling:\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"tel:5638886477\\\">(563) 888-6477<\\/a> | Illinois\\/Iowa\\r\\n<a href=\\\"tel:8558922420\\\">(855) 892-2420<\\/a> | Texas\\r\\n<a href=\\\"tel:8448242265\\\">(844) 824-2265<\\/a> | Colorado, Kansas &amp; New Mexico\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/expand-block {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc136f21e14\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/expand-block\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"expand_trigger\": \"Contact Us\",\n        \"_expand_trigger\": \"field_5f92144be93f6\",\n        \"expand_content\": \"<h4>Our Customer Care Teams Are Ready To Assist<\\/h4>\\r\\n<strong>Customer Care <a href=\\\"tel:8666443935\\\">866-644-3935<\\/a><\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you have questions about your account, services or alternative ways to bank, please feel free to contact the Customer Care Center. Please expect longer than normal wait times as we are currently experiencing higher than usual call volume.\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Treasury Management Customers<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you have any questions about your account, please reach out to your banker directly or contact your local treasury management support team:\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"tel:5638886477\\\">563-888-6477<\\/a> | Illinois\\/Iowa\\r\\n<a href=\\\"tel:8558922420\\\">855-892-2420<\\/a> | Texas\\r\\n<a href=\\\"tel:8448242265\\\">844-824-2265<\\/a> | Colorado, Kansas &amp; New Mexico\\r\\n\\r\\n<strong>Commercial Loan Customers<\\/strong>\\r\\n\\r\\nIf you have questions about your commercial loans with TBK Bank or would like to discuss available payment options, please contact your banker to help guide you through the process.\\r\\n\\r\\n<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/paybill.com\\/consumer\\/?ClientId=TBKBank\\\">Make a loan payment online directly from our website<\\/a>.\",\n        \"_expand_content\": \"field_5f92145ae93f7\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"left\",\n    \"mode\": \"edit\"\n} /-->\n<!-- /wp:acf/wrapper -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/wrapper {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc13f121e15\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/wrapper\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"generous_vertical_padding\": \"0\",\n        \"_generous_vertical_padding\": \"field_5f6e04852a13b\",\n        \"show_layout_options\": \"1\",\n        \"_show_layout_options\": \"field_5f579b546ee17\",\n        \"width\": \"container-md\",\n        \"_width\": \"field_5f5798a171a9f\",\n        \"background_color\": \"white\",\n        \"_background_color\": \"field_5f57993c71aa0\"\n    },\n    \"align\": \"\",\n    \"mode\": \"preview\"\n} -->\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>PROTECTING YOUR FINANCES</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Updated Contact Info</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Help us stay in touch with you by making sure your personal information such as email address and phone number is up to date in our system. You can update this information in online banking.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Fraud Prevention</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Your financial well-being is important to us. We want to protect your personal information, good credit and your money from scams. To help keep you informed, we encourage you to read the following tips and ways to avoid fraud.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"/fraud-prevention/\">TBK Bank Fraud Prevention</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Wire Transfers</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TBK Bank can wire money where it needs to be quickly, easily and safely. To anyone, anywhere in the world.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"/business/services/wiring-instructions/\">TBK Bank Wire Instructions</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":60} -->\n<div style=\"height:60px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2>PROTECTING YOUR FUNDS</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:spacer {\"height\":20} -->\n<div style=\"height:20px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n<!-- /wp:spacer -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>There’s no need to withdraw large amounts of cash or take other extreme financial measures. The best place for your money is in a safe, sound financial institution, where it is insured by the FDIC. TBK remains financially sound. Find out more about our parent company, Triumph Bancorp, our values and our commitments to our communities, please visit our investor relations web site. You can also find more information about:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"http://ir.triumphbancorp.com/Docs\">Financial Condition and Performance</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://ir.triumphbancorp.com/financial-info/sec-filings/sec-filings-details/default.aspx?FilingId=13905062\">10-K Report</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4} -->\n<h4>Key Statistics</h4>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>As of December 31, 2019, our capital ratios exceeded those levels necessary to be categorized as “well capitalized” under the regulatory framework for prompt corrective action.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Total Assets:&nbsp;<strong>$5.1 billion</strong><br>Total Deposits:&nbsp;<strong>$3.8 billion</strong><br>Total Loans:&nbsp;<strong>$4.2 billion</strong><br>Market Capitalization:&nbsp;<strong>$1.0 billion</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>TBK Bank is a wholly owned subsidiary of Triumph Bancorp, Inc.</strong><br>Consolidated Reports of Condition and Income for TBK Bank filed with the FDIC is available at&nbsp;<a href=\"https://research2.fdic.gov/bankfind/\">https://research2.fdic.gov/bankfind/</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>TBK Bank’s FDIC Certificate # is 23498.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- /wp:acf/wrapper -->\n\n<!-- wp:acf/banner {\n    \"id\": \"block_5fbc151021e16\",\n    \"name\": \"acf\\/banner\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"alignment\": \"center\",\n        \"_alignment\": \"field_5f8f4c162afd4\",\n        \"copy\": \"<h2>Open An Account With TBK Bank<\\/h2>\\r\\nA better banking experience is a few clicks away.\",\n        \"_copy\": \"field_5f57ece16621e\",\n        \"links_0_link\": {\n            \"title\": \"Open An Account\",\n            \"url\": \"\\/our-bank\\/apply-for-an-account\\/\",\n            \"target\": \"\"\n        },\n        \"_links_0_link\": \"field_5f60b46f4693f\",\n        \"links_0_link_color\": \"primary\",\n        \"_links_0_link_color\": \"field_5f60b46f46940\",\n        \"links_0_link_style\": \"solid\",\n        \"_links_0_link_style\": \"field_5f60b46f46941\",\n        \"links\": 1,\n        \"_links\": \"field_5f60b46f4693e\",\n        \"is_row\": \"0\",\n        \"_is_row\": \"field_5f60b258214a8\",\n        \"show_app